overview.longBusinessSummary: Vornado Realty Trust (Vornado) is a fully-integrated real estate investment trust (REIT) and conducts its business through, and substantially all of its interests in properties are held by, Vornado Realty L.P. (the Operating Partnership), a Delaware limited partnership. Vornado is the sole general partner of and owned approximately 91.4% of the common limited partnership interest in the Operating Partnership as of June 30, 2025. All references to the Company, we, us and our mean, collectively, Vornado, the Operating Partnership and those subsidiaries consolidated by Vornado.
